                                <img src="/images/network.png" style="max-width: 100%;">
                                <h1 style="font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">NETWORKS</h1>

                                <p>
                                    Networks allow you to create groups that hold ownership over Acid Blocks, Snitch Blocks, Bastion Blocks and Factories.
                                    You can invite as many players to your network as you want and you can be in as many networks as you want too.
                                </p>

                                <p style="margin-top: 16px;">
                                    You can control every members network permission to give individual players as much or as little control over your network as you please.
                                </p>

                                <p>
                                    Networks do not prevent you from attacking each other and there is no indicator as to who which network.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-sm">
                                <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
                                    <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/l7iSOMWphFg" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                </div>

                                <h5 style="margin-top: 8px;">Commands</h5>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network create &lt;name&gt;</kbd> - Create a new network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network invite &lt;network&gt; &lt;username&gt;</kbd> - Invite a player to your network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network join &lt;network&gt;</kbd> - Join a network that as invited you</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network join &lt;network&gt; [password]</kbd> - Join a network using a Password</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network pending</kbd> - View all of your pending network invitations</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network deny &lt;network&gt;</kbd> - Deny an invitation to join a network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network password &lt;network&gt; &lt;password&gt;</kbd> - Change your network password</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network playerlist &lt;network&gt;</kbd> - View your networks member list</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network permission &lt;network&gt; &lt;username&gt;</kbd> - Edit a members permissions</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network delete &lt;network&gt;</kbd> - Delete your network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network uninvite &lt;network&gt; &lt;username&gt;</kbd> - Revoke a players invitation</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network leave &lt;network&gt;</kbd> - Leave a network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network kick &lt;network&gt; &lt;username&gt;</kbd> - Kick a player from the network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network rename &lt;network&gt; &lt;name&gt;</kbd> - Rename your network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network list</kbd> - List all networks you are a member of</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network rally</kbd> - Broadcast your location to your network</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;"><kbd>/network help [page]</kbd> - View a list of these commands in-game</p>
                            </div>
